;--[[
; Tronex
; 2019/8/16
; Added global precoditions for upgrade sections, instead of using huge ass list for each mechanic and every single upgrade
; In other words: you can set a common upgrade precodition for every mechanic with no need to define the whole upgrade sections in the files
; Example: tier 1 upgrades require basic toolkits to be delivered to a mechenic who has parameter: "def_upgr_tier_1 = 0"

; The following parameters are used to assign global condition to upgrades for a mechanic
; And of course, you can make custom ones inside mechanic's file just like the old way, and they will override global precoditions

; Parameters:
; def_upgr_tier_1 = n	  ; tier 1 upgrades
; def_upgr_tier_2 = n     ; tier 2 upgrades
; def_upgr_tier_3 = n     ; tier 3 upgrades

; Values:
; n = 0 (requires mechanics to have the matching toolkit, keep in mind this is handled usually by toolkits quests that trigger info portion for the mechanic)
; n = 1 (permanently locked)
; n = 2 (permanently unlocked)


;--]]

